00:40:31.306 --> 00:40:32.900
You still have to give off heat.

00:40:32.900 --> 00:40:34.000
You still have to
degrade energy.

00:40:34.000 --> 00:40:36.291
You still have to have an
energy source and degrade it.

00:40:36.291 --> 00:40:39.560
So he had these scales
of civilizations.

00:40:39.560 --> 00:40:42.280
He said a Type I
civilization was

00:40:42.280 --> 00:40:45.010
one that harnessed the energy
of its home planet, a Type

00:40:45.010 --> 00:40:47.970
II, its home star, a Type
