surrounded with technology.

00:41:39.700 --> 00:41:44.790
So, hard to tell that
apart from a dead star,

00:41:44.790 --> 00:41:47.520
which is also going to give off
a lot of heat and be very dark.

00:41:47.520 --> 00:41:53.380
